<h2>Query Volume Statistics</h2>
<p><strong>15. Monthly queries hit 780 million as of May 2025.</strong>
Source: Perplexity CEO Aravind Srinivas.
That is a 3x increase from 250 million monthly queries in July 2024.</p>
<p><strong>16. Daily queries range between 35 and 45 million in early 2026.</strong>
Source: Index.dev, 2026.
The company reported approximately 30 million daily queries in May 2025.</p>
<p><strong>17. Weekly queries reached 100 million in April 2025.</strong>
Source: Perplexity CEO public statement, April 2025.
That equals roughly 14 million queries per day.</p>
<p><strong>18. Perplexity processed 500 million queries in the entire year of 2023.</strong>
Source: DemandSage, 2023.
The platform now handles more queries in a single month than it did in all of 2023.</p>
<p><strong>19. Projected monthly queries for mid-2026 range from 1.2 to 1.5 billion.</strong>
Source: Incremys, 2026 estimate.
If the growth rate holds, Perplexity could process 50 million queries per day by summer 2026.</p>
<p>These query numbers still represent a small share of overall search. Google processes roughly 14 billion queries per day. But the growth trajectory is significant for anyone tracking <a href="/blog/ai-search-market-share/">AI search market share</a>.</p>
