<h2>Revenue and Valuation Statistics</h2>
<p><strong>20. Annual recurring revenue grew from $5 million (2022) to $200 million (February 2026).</strong>
Source: DemandSage / Wikipedia, multiple dates.
That is a 40x increase in under 4 years.</p>
<p><strong>21. ARR reached $80 million by late 2024.</strong>
Source: DemandSage / Wikipedia, late 2024.
Revenue more than doubled from $10 million in 2023.</p>
<p><strong>22. Perplexity targets $656 million in ARR for 2026.</strong>
Source: DemandSage, 2026 projection.
Reaching that number would require roughly 3x growth from the February 2026 baseline.</p>
<p><strong>23. Valuation grew from $121 million (March 2023) to $21.2 billion (early 2026).</strong>
Source: Tracxn, multiple funding rounds.
That is a 175x increase in less than 3 years.</p>
