<h2>FAQ</h2>
<p><strong>How many users does Perplexity AI have in 2026?</strong></p>
<p>Perplexity AI has approximately 45 million monthly active users as of early 2026. Daily active users number around 2 million. The platform receives 5.6 million average daily visitors and 170 million monthly website visits according to Similarweb data.</p>
<p><strong>How much revenue does Perplexity AI generate?</strong></p>
<p>Perplexity AI reached $200 million in annual recurring revenue by February 2026. The company targets $656 million ARR by the end of 2026. Revenue grew from $5 million in 2022 to $80 million in late 2024, then more than doubled in 2025.</p>
<p><strong>How does Perplexity compare to ChatGPT in size?</strong></p>
<p>ChatGPT dominates with 82.6% of the AI chatbot market and 900 million weekly active users. Perplexity holds 6.4% to 8% market share with 45 million MAU. However, Perplexity grew at 800% year over year, making it the fastest-growing AI search platform. For a deeper comparison, see our <a href="/blog/chatgpt-vs-claude-seo/">ChatGPT vs Claude for SEO</a> analysis.</p>
<p><strong>Is Perplexity AI profitable?</strong></p>
<p>Perplexity AI has not publicly confirmed profitability. With $200 million ARR and significant infrastructure costs for AI model inference, the company likely operates at a loss. Its $1.72 billion in funding provides a long runway. The $656 million 2026 revenue target suggests a focus on growth over near-term profitability.</p>
<p><strong>How does Perplexity AI affect SEO?</strong></p>
<p>Perplexity cites web sources inline and drives referral traffic to websites it quotes. Optimizing for Perplexity involves structured content, clear answers, and authoritative sourcing. This falls under <a href="/glossary/answer-engine-optimization/">answer engine optimization</a>. Our guide on <a href="/blog/optimize-for-perplexity-ai/">how to optimize for Perplexity AI</a> covers specific tactics. For more on the broader shift, explore our <a href="/best/ai-seo-tools/">best AI SEO tools</a> roundup.</p>
